      <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-3 md:mb-4">🏆</div>
      <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold mb-2 md:mb-3">Make Better Decisions</h3>
      <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600">
        Use consensus rankings to optimize your transfers, captain picks, and chip strategy.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

